              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#111112"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2" color="#FFF8DC">
                <p>You can easily add a hyperlink to your message.</p><br />
                <p>All that you need to do is type the URL (http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/), and it will automatically be converted to a URL (<span class="spnMessageText"><a href="http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/" target="_blank">http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/</a></span>)!</p><br />
                <p>The trick here is to make sure you prefix your URL with the <b>http://</b>, <b>https://</b> or <b>file://</b></p><br />
                <p>You can also add a mailto link to your message by typing in your e-mail address.<br />
                <blockquote>
                       <i>This Example:</i><br />
                       <b>arcastar@finalcovenant.dhs.org</b><br />
                       <i>Outputs this:</i><br />
                       <span class="spnMessageText"><a href="mailto:arcastar@finalcovenant.dhs.org">arcastar@finalcovenant.dhs.org</a></span></p>
                </blockquote><br />
                <p>Another way to add hyperlinks is to use the <b>[url]</b>linkto<b>[/url]</b> tags</p>
                <blockquote>
                       <i>This Example:</i><br />
                       <b>[url]</b>http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/<b>[/url]</b> takes you home!<br />
                       <i>Outputs This:</i><br />
                       <span class="spnMessageText"><a href="http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/">http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/</a></span> takes you home!
                </blockquote></p>
                <p>
                <p>If you use this tag: <b>[url=&quot;</b>linkto<b>&quot;]</b>description<b>[/url]</b> you can add a description to the link.</p>
                <blockquote>
                       <i>This Example:</i><br />
                       Take me to <b>[url=&quot;http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/&quot;]</b>The Final Covenant<b>[/url]</b><br />
                       <i>Outputs This:</i><br />
                       Take me to <span class="spnMessageText"><a href="http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/">The Final Covenant</a></span>
                </blockquote>
                <blockquote>
                       <i>This Example:</i><br />
                       If you have a question <b>[url=&quot;arcastar@finalcovenant.dhs.org&quot;]</b>E-Mail Me<b>[/url]</b><br />
                       <i>Outputs This:</i><br />
                       If you have a question <span class="spnMessageText"><a href="mailto:arcastar@finalcovenant.dhs.org">E-Mail Me</a></span>
                </blockquote>
                <br />
                You can make clickable images by combining the <b>[url="</b>linkto<b>"]</b>description<b>[/url]</b> and <b>[img]</b>image_url<b>[/img]</b> tags<br />
                <blockquote>
                       <i>This Example:</i><br />
                       <b>[url=&quot;http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/&quot;][img]</b>/fctitle3.jpg<b>[/img][/url]</b><br />
                       <i>Outputs This:</i><br />
                       <a href="http://finalcovenant.dhs.org/forum/" target="_blank"><img src="/fctitle3.jpg" border="0" alt="" title="" /></a>
                </blockquote>
                </p>
                </font></td>
